chart.name: Total CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('cpuUtilization.kern').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('cpuUtilization.user', filter=filter('EngineName', 'SqlServer')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+B).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).min().publish(label='D')
E = (C).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='E')
F = (C).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='F')
G = (C).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='G')
H = (C).max().publish(label='H')

chart.name: % Storage Used
chart.programText:
A = data('disks.usedPc').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: % Active Memory
chart.programText:
A = data('memory.physAvailKb').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memory.physTotKb').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = ((B-A)/B).scale(100).publish(label='C', enable=False)
M = (C).min().publish(label='M')
I = (C).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='I')
J = (C).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='J')
K = (C).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='K')
L = (C).max().publish(label='L')

chart.name: Network Traffic (bytes/sec)
chart.programText:
G = data('network.rdBytesPS').publish(label='G', enable=False)
A = data('network.wrBytesPS').publish(label='A', enable=False)
H = (G+A).publish(label='H', enable=False)
B = (H).min().publish(label='B')
C = (H).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (H).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (H).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (H).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Total CPU Utilization %

chart.name: Read Throughput

F = (A).max().publish(label='F')
